

# Potter Portfolio Website

A modern, elegant and fully responsive portfolio website for a professional potter and ceramic artist.  
This project includes animations, a blog, client testimonials, and showcases ceramic works in a clean and visually appealing layout.

---

# üá¨üáß English Version

## Features

- Fully responsive layout  
- Clean and modern design  
- Swiper.js sliders (gallery, testimonials, blog)  
- GSAP animations  
- Blog pages  
- Optimized HTML/CSS structure  
- Great performance on mobile and desktop  
- Simple deployment via GitHub Pages  

---

## Tech Stack

- HTML5  
- CSS3 / SCSS  
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)  
- Swiper.js  
- GSAP (GreenSock)  
- GitHub Pages  

---

## Installation & Usage

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/GioGall1/potter-portfolio.git
```

2. Navigate into the folder:
```bash
cd potter-portfolio
```

3. Open `index.html` in any browser.

---

## Deploying to GitHub Pages

1. Go to **Settings ‚Üí Pages**  
2. Choose branch: `main`  
3. Folder: `/root`  
4. Save  

Your website will be available at:

```
https://giogall1.github.io/potter-portfolio/
```

---

